{"tid":1891541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麥美娟：我哋啲口罩 係只送不賣嘅！！","createTime":"2020-02-22T02:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T16:12:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":396,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba6ef3dc449ef4cfc7d02953c7e672fc7eb6514","tid":1891541,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"邱騰華：設本地生產線有儲備是好事<br />\n<br />\n在會上麥美娟提到，工聯會自設口罩工廠生產時，根本不知有此基金，他們成立工廠是不想坐等政府援手，「我哋係只送不賣嘅！」，麥美娟稱未知會否申請基金。她指有投資者想注資生產口罩，向生產力促進局詢問卻未有提供協助，結果他把生產線轉到澳門，希望政府向有心人提供技術支援，以及設立「口罩生產熱線」援助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/財委會-59-票通過-300-億抗疫防疫基金-陳志全鄭松泰朱凱廸投反對票\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-59-%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-300-%E5%84%84%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E9%99%B3%E5%BF%97%E5%85%A8%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8%E6%8A%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%A5%A8&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=50308b5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-59-%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-300-%E5%84%84%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E9%99%B3%E5%BF%97%E5%85%A8%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0%E6%9C%B1%E5%87%B1%E5%BB%B8%E6%8A%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%A5%A8&h=1e3e9155\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/財委會-59-票通過-300-億抗疫防疫基金-陳志全鄭松泰朱凱廸投反對票</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9aeda72bd16f6db5dab53be4228cd841b8d013","tid":1891541,"uid":87780,"like":192,"dislike":1,"score":191,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"出廿萬一個月俾你呢個廢人仲有撚用呀<br />\nfailed state <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e78d6b784e65a5a5539d354adfd122eba